message:
{{#is_alert}}
🔴 [P1 CRITICAL] ArgoCD work queue depth is above 100

Queue depth: {{value}}
The controller is falling behind processing applications. This indicates the controller cannot keep up with the number of apps or reconciliation events.

Actions:
1. Check controller pod resources (CPU/memory) on Host Cluster dashboard
2. Check if reconciliation is slow (p95 duration)
3. Look for a surge in git changes or ApplicationSet generator changes
4. Consider scaling controller resources or sharding
{{/is_alert}}
